It's the final issue for Young Avengers! It was a great run while it lasted, and at least it's wrapping up while it's still a great title. Also-- Marvel UK's heroes are getting the spotlight shone on them once more. Hooray! Captain Britan, Pete Wisdom and the fine young animals at MI-13 are joined by Death's Head II for some majick-y, Albion-y shenanigans.

If you like them and have the money, BUY THEM and support your favorite creators, writers, artists, local comic shops and publishers. All my thanks to all the uploaders and scanners and seeders out there! Enjoy! (and seed!)
